# TowerOS UI/UX Theme Rules

TowerOS is an enterprise telecom SaaS platform.

The design style must prioritize:
- simplicity
- speed
- operational clarity
- usability
- low cognitive load
- enterprise professionalism

The UI should feel like:
- Microsoft Azure Portal
- ServiceNow
- Atlassian Jira
- Linear
- Grafana

NOT:
- flashy startup landing pages
- excessive animations
- glassmorphism-heavy UI
- neon cyberpunk themes
- cluttered ERP systems

---

# DESIGN PHILOSOPHY

Use "Operational Minimalism"

Meaning:
- clean layouts
- spacious design
- readable typography
- fast workflows
- data-first interfaces
- map-first architecture
- low-click actions
- clear hierarchy

